{"tid":2371241,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"蜉蝣同飛蛾的故事","createTime":"2021-01-18T16:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T16:37:25.000Z","uid":344609,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b7c3e17b04db96eb40d702153636ad3da5582702","tid":2371241,"uid":344609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:07:30.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-small\">From《舉重妖精金福珠》女主角失戀嗰陣佢同自己講嘅對白</span><br />\n<br />\n某一天，蜉蝣看見飛蛾嘗試飛去營火，<br />\n<br />\n蜉蝣對着飛蛾如此說道：<br />\n<br />\n「你明知道那道火光是人類設下的陷阱，你又不像我只能活一天，為什麼明知道會死掉卻還是要撲上去呢？」<br />\n<br />\n飛蛾如此回答：「那道火光太過漂亮了，我被它深深吸引着了，我無法克制自己不撲上去。世上沒有任何美麗是未經痛苦而成的。」<br />\n<br />\n然後，蜉蝣眼巴巴看着飛蛾朝火道的方向飛了，而蜉蝣選擇留在原本的地方直到生命離它而去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77edeb92ee88ae2bd77786294e81d5a9905b3549","tid":2371241,"uid":242358,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:07:53.000Z","msg":"嘩好好睇"},{"pid":"13a5b5f9f391d146155cd2028d13d4a0ba749d9e","tid":2371241,"uid":217283,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:13:01.000Z","msg":"咁我算咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202b0943cdbc4b51bdd8bf1f60e98f4fd86dc6ae","tid":2371241,"uid":347610,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:15:50.000Z","msg":"有動力繼續堅持了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7420ad0d28004d4cc9e82a57af2556319d59b605","tid":2371241,"uid":344609,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:22:56.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f324966d88b883d93c441e76178d6caefa9928a6","tid":2371241,"uid":311122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"世上沒有任何美麗是未經痛苦而成的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e361db25e8a79ea2864bd1cf49b227029637bbd","tid":2371241,"uid":117091,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f324966d88b883d93c441e76178d6caefa9928a6","tid":2371241,"uid":311122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"世上沒有任何美麗是未經痛苦而成的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:37:25.000Z","msg":"有。我就係！"}]}